# Gestalt — Cursor agent entrypoint

Project AI guardrails are modular Markdown rules under `.cursor/rules/` (`.mdc` files with YAML frontmatter).

Before writing or refactoring **execution code** (runtime paths, crew wiring, tools, integrations):

1. Read **`core.mdc`** — Python standards and test-driven workflow.
2. Read **`request.mdc`** — define contracts before new features.
3. Read **`refresh.mdc`** — use the structured crash pipeline from `debug/crash_report.template.md` when debugging.

Plain copies for humans live in the same folder as **`core.md`**, **`request.md`**, **`refresh.md`** (no frontmatter).
